Mexico ' s Blanco predicts August CPI at 1 . 3 pct . Mexican Commerce Minister Herminio Blanco on Friday forecast August inflation of about 1 . 3 percent . " We have half the inflation we had a year ago and we expect that for the month of August we will have inflation close to 1 . 3 percent , " Blanco said during testimony to Mexico ' s Congress . Banco de Mexico is expected to release August inflation data on Monday . A Reuters survey of local economists MXAAP forecast August inflation of 1 . 36 percent . Blanco told legislators that Mexico had emerged from its economic crisis and was on the road to recovery . - - Claudia Villegas , Mexico City Newsroom 525 7289549 
